These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, pumpkin
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, dancing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, satire
1. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person eating pumpkin##8
2. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | water     | almond-milk      |
| Food          | pumpkin | lettuce    |
| Hobby         | dancing   | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | satire      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, chess
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, writer
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
3. the writer is not to the right of the lawyer##8
4. the person driving the jet-ski is not the person who's hobby is chess##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | sprite        | coffee    |
| Hobby       | photography         | chess |
| Job         | writer | lawyer   |
| Transport   | jet-ski               | trike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, superhero
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, salsa
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, italian
2 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish
1. the spanish is in an odd position##4
2. the italian is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery       | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | salsa    |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian |
| Pet           | hamster        | goldfish   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
