The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, photographer
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, nigerian
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, jet-ski
1. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | reading | gardening  |
| Job           | photographer  | bartender |
| Nationality   | nigerian | brazilian   |
| Transport     | jet-ski   | snowmobile |

