.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, tomato
The people have 2 different hobbies: jet-skid-games, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, pilot
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane
1. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
5. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person eating tomato##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | raspberry | tomato            |
| Hobby       | woodworking | jet-skid-games              |
| Job         | scientist  | pilot |
| Transport   | jet-ski     | airplane         |

