There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, german
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person driving the boat is not the person watching western movies##6
4. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | scientific |
| Nationality   | chinese    | german   |
| Sport         | badminton | cycling     |
| Transport     | skateboard | boat  |

